Completed Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Physics, Aerospace, or similar;
Understand software development, especially Agile and DevSecOps approach;
Skilled in Python, Java, and Rust;
A willingness to work with a multi-disciplinary team where you are the security engineer that doesn’t just say “no” when presented with a problem;
A team player who can work well with non-security experts;
Research- & innovation-minded;
Proficient in English and Dutch.
